990/SMHI_month_year_normal_61_90_precipitation_mm.txt | title=Precipitation Normals 1961–1990 (Swedish) | publisher =Swedish Metereological and Hydrological Institute (Gotska Sandön code 8924) | language = }}</ref> |source 2 = SMHI Monthly Data 2002–2015<ref name=eather2>{{cite web | url=http://www.smhi.se/klimatdata/meteorologi/temperatur/2.1240 | title=Monthly and Yearly Statistics (Swedish) | publisher = SMHI| date= April 17, 2016}}</ref> |date=April 2016}} {{clear}} {{Swedish National Parks}}
